Package: neuroim
Imports:
    Matrix,
    yaImpute,
    assertthat
License: GPL (>= 2)
Maintainer: Bradley Buchsbaum <brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com>
Title: neuroim: R software for reading, writing and representing brain imaging
    data.
Type: Package
Author: Bradley R. Buchsbaum
Description: neuroim is a collection of data structures that represent
    volumetric brain imaging data. The focus is on basic data handling for 3D
    and 4D neuroimaging data. In addition, there are function to read and write
    ANALYZE7.5 and NIFTI files and limited support for reading AFNI files.
Version: 0.0.3
Date: 2014-04-01
Suggests:
    testthat
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0),
    stringr,
    hash,
    iterators,
    abind,
    methods
Collate:
    'AFNI_IO.R'
